No. 09-10876. Donald Bullcoming, Petitioner v. New Mexico. 562 U.S. 1028, 131 S. Ct. 587,

178 L. Ed. 2d 412,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8709. November 8, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for appointment of counsel granted. Jeffrey L. Fisher, Esquire, of Stanford, California, is appointed to serve as counsel for the petitioner in this case.
